user_review: Good Taouk    If you are up in the plateau and are craving good shish taouk, fast, head to this place. Corner Mount-Royal and The Main   I like the  chicken shawarma wrap, with garlic, hummus and hot sauce, an order of there ridiculous roasted potatoes(smothered in garlic sauce) and of course, washed down with black cherry soda. They call it a 'trio" in Canada   This place also has a butt load of windows along the wall so it is a great place to people watch...if you're into that.wakawaka
Great tasting food with very friendly service. Standard menu options of Mediterranean foods to choose from.
Very good food. Very good prices. Very nice environment. And extremely friendly staff! One of my favorite halal food places in Montreal.

Excellent shawarma .. We can from Pennsylvania to check out Montreal and we found this nice restaurant. The food quality is excellent and the prices are reasonable. Excellent middle eastern food for sure.
I go hear often for lunch. Quick service and good food. Cannot beat the price for this area.

Great late night spot if you are around the Mont Royal/Saint Laurent intersection. The owner is a really nice guy who goes the extra distance to make sure every customer is happy. Great variety of salads and good prices for shawarmas.  Spécial trio is a good deal. The fries are very good.
Delicious. I had the chicken shawarma and it was fantastic. The staff were very friendly. I'll definitely be back.
